OL,3,CHospital porters to strike over
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment'
OL,6,FSome porters at the NHS Trust which
OL,7,Fruns Southampton General Hospital are
OL,8,Fto go on strike over claims of
OL,9,F"bullying and harassment".
OL,11,FMore than 60 porters employed by
OL,12,FUniversity Hospital Southampton NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust, who are members of
OL,14,FUnite the Union, will walkout on 17
OL,15,Fseparate dates.
OL,17,FThe first 24 hour walkout will take
OL,18,Fplace on Thursday 28 November. Each
OL,19,Fstrike day will begin at 06:00 and end
OL,20,Fat 05:59 the following day.
