OL,4,C'bullying and harassment'
OL,6,FThis will then be followed by strikes
OL,7,Fon Monday and Friday each week
OL,8,Fthroughout December and January.
OL,10,FUnite the Union claims that hospital
OL,11,Fporters are subjected to restricted
OL,12,Ftoilet breaks and are denied rest
OL,13,Fbreaks to sit down and drink water.
