OL,3,CHospital porters to strike over
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment'
OL,6,FUniversity Hospital Southampton NHS
OL,7,FFoundation Trust says "there isn't,
OL,8,Fand never has been, a requirement for
OL,9,Fany member of our staff to ask
OL,10,Fpermission to take a bathroom break"
OL,11,Fwith porters "actively encouraged to
OL,12,Fstay hydrated using any of the water
OL,13,Fcooler facilities" throughout its
OL,14,Fhospitals.
OL,16,FThe NHS Trust has commissioned an
OL,17,F"independent external review, seeking
OL,18,Fviews of all the portering department"
OL,19,Fto support its "ongoing efforts to
OL,20,Faddress issues raised".
