OL,3,CHospital porters to strike over
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment'
OL,6,FSharon Graham, General Secretary,
OL,7,FUnite the Union, said: "Our
OL,8,FSouthampton hospital porters have
OL,9,Fstood up and made it completely clear
OL,10,Fthey will not tolerate bullying and
OL,11,Fharassment any longer.
OL,13,F"It is shameful that even when
OL,14,Fpresented with the facts, hospital
OL,15,Fmanagement has failed to act to end
OL,16,Fthe abuse.
OL,18,F"Unite's laser-like focus on the jobs,
OL,19,Fpay and conditions of its members will
OL,20,Fmean that our porters will receive the
OL,21,Funion's absolute support."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
