OL,6,FSteve Harris, chief people officer at
OL,7,FUniversity Hospital Southampton NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust (UHS), said: "Our
OL,9,Fportering service and colleagues are a
OL,10,Fvaluable and intrinsic part of the
OL,11,Fsuccessful running of UHS and all we
OL,12,Fdo for patients.
OL,14,F"Prior to the ballot, and having been
OL,15,Fmade aware of staff concerns, the
OL,16,FTrust commissioned an independent
OL,17,Fexternal review, seeking views of all
OL,18,Fthe portering department. When we
OL,19,Freceive this report, the outcomes from
OL,20,Fit will support our ongoing efforts to
OL,21,Faddress issues raised.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
