OL,3,CHospital porters to strike over
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment'
OL,6,F"We have been in direct contact,
OL,7,Fverbally and in writing, with Unite
OL,8,Fand our portering staff to reassure
OL,9,Fthem on a few specific concerns raised
OL,10,Frelating to claims made around Trust
OL,11,Fpolicy.
OL,13,F"Regarding breaks, we have reiterated
OL,14,Fon many occasions to our porters that
OL,15,Fthere isn't, and never has been, a
OL,16,Frequirement for any member of our
OL,17,Fstaff to ask permission to take a
OL,18,Fbathroom break.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
