OL,3,CHospital porters to strike over
OL,4,C'bullying and harassment'
OL,6,F"Our porters are entitled to three
OL,7,Fofficial breaks during every shift and
OL,8,Fare actively encouraged to stay
OL,9,Fhydrated using any of the water cooler
OL,10,Ffacilities throughout our hospitals.
OL,12,F"At UHS we want everyone who works
OL,13,Fhere to feel they belong, are valued,
OL,14,Frespected and heard.
OL,16,F"We remain in active discussions with
OL,17,FUnite and local portering
OL,18,Frepresentatives to address the issues
OL,19,Fbeing raised and will continue to work
OL,20,Fconstructively to resolve the dispute.
